snippet.title: Ashes of Oahu - Announcement
snippet.description:
An open world, post-apocalyptic RPG shooter where you tap into the power of the spirit world to liberate the Hawaiian island of Oahu from the army that occupies it.

WEBSITE
Pre-Orders now available at:
https://www.ashesofoahu.com/

STEAM
Store : https://store.steampowered.com/app/671600/Ashes_of_Oahu/
Community: https://steamcommunity.com/app/671600/discussions/
News: https://steamcommunity.com/app/671600/allnews/

SOCIAL MEDIA

FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/AshesofOahu/
